                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5165" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0756</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8359 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管理新赋能：业财融合下动力源求新求变之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A new way of Empowering Management: The Journey of Innovating and Changing made by DPC under the Business-finance integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱莲美，郑思敏，胡一元</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国矿业大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京动力源科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">销售业务系统；业财融合；业务流程再造；财务转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sales business system; Business-finance integration; Business processing planning; Financial transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着云计算、移动互联网等信息技术的广泛应用和企业管理思想的不断创新，财务管理将从价值守护者转向价值创造者，更多的精力投入到业务支持和战略决策支持中。本案例涉及的北京动力源科技股份有限公司（DPC）正处在这样的转型中。面对竞争激烈的商业环境，北京动力源科技股份有限公司（DPC）以优化内部管理流程和制度、强化决策支持、高效利用资产创造企业价值为目的，以服务客户为宗旨，建立一套以管理+流程+考核为一体的业务系统。本案例介绍了动力源公司销售业务系统的建设过程，具体阐述了业务系统的建设动因、建设目标、业务流程梳理、功能板块设计，保障因素分析等内容。本案例拟引导财务工作更好地和业务管理相融合，提供深入价值链的业务支持，面向业务经营，提供财务服务，从单纯的“计算器”转型成企业的“导航仪”，并对其他业务相似性的企业建设销售业务系统提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the wide application of cloud computing, mobile Internet and other information technologies and the continuous innovation of enterprise management thoughts, financial management will shift from value guardian to value creator, and more energy will be put into business support and strategic decision support. The case involved in Beijing Power Source Technology Co., Ltd. (DPC) is in such a transformation.Facing the competitive business environment, DPC aims to optimize the internal management process and system, strengthen decision support, make efficient use of assets, and create enterprise value for the goal, to serve customers for the purpose, to establish a set of management + process + assessment as one of the business system. This case introduces the construction process of the sales business system of the power source company, and elaborates the construction motivation, construction objective, business process combing, functional section design, guarantee factor analysis and other contents of the business system. This case intends to guide financial work to better integrate with business management, provide in-depth value chain business support, business-oriented operations, provide financial services, from a simple &quot;calculator&quot; to an enterprise &quot;navigator&quot;, and provide reference for other similar enterprises to build sales business system.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级管理会计》、《高级财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业财融合、销售业务系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-02</td>
                            </tr>
